<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Reservation Status Update: CANCELLED</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            color: #333;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        h2 {
            color: #e74c3c;
            text-align: center;
        }

        p {
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #777;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Reservation Status Update: CANCELLED</h2>
        <p>Hello Admin,</p>
        <p>A reservation with the following details has been <strong>CANCELLED</strong> by the user: <%= user.email %></p>
        <p>The reservation was made on <%= reservation.createdAt %>.</p>

        <ul>
            <li><strong>Reservation ID:</strong> <%= reservation.id %></li>
            <li><strong>Name:</strong>  <%= user.firstName %> <%= user.lastName %></li>
            <li><strong>Email:</strong>  <%= user.email %></li>
            <li><strong>Phone:</strong>  <%= user.phone %></li>
            <li><strong>Pick-Up Date:</strong> <%= reservation.pickDate %></li>
            <li><strong>Drop-Off Date:</strong> <%= reservation.dropDate %></li>
            <li><strong>Pick-Up Location:</strong> <%= reservation.pickUp %></li>
            <li><strong>Drop-Off Location:</strong> <%= reservation.dropOff %></li>
            <li><strong>Vehicle:</strong> <%= vehicle.name %></li>
            <li><strong>Total Price:</strong> <%= reservation.totalPrice %></li>
            <li><strong>Unit:</strong> <%= reservation.unit %></li>
            <li><strong>Passenger:</strong> <%= reservation.passengers %></li>
        </ul>

        <p>If you have any questions or need further information, please contact the user.</p>
        <p>Thank you.</p>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>This email is sent to notify you of the cancellation. If you have any concerns, please contact the user directly.</p>
            <img src="https://bangteg.github.io/images/dampit-trans-logo.png" alt="Company Logo" style="max-width: 100px;">
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>
